</h3>
      <div class="gem-c-image-card__description"><div class="govspeak">
<p>Farmers and land managers applying for BPS and claiming for CS and ES payments are urged to do so in good time ahead of the 15 May deadline.</p>
</div></div>


    </div>
  </div>

