              <a class="gem-c-image-card__title-link brand__color" href="/government/news/countryside-stewardship-opens-for-applications-in-2019">Countryside Stewardship opens for applications in 2019</a>
</h3>
      <div class="gem-c-image-card__description"><div class="govspeak">
