              <a class="gem-c-image-card__title-link brand__color" href="/guidance/cross-compliance-2019">Cross compliance 2019</a>
</h3>
      <div class="gem-c-image-card__description"><div class="govspeak">
<p>Farmers and land managers must follow these cross compliance rules from 1 January 2019 if they claim for the Basic Payment Scheme (BPS), a stewardship scheme or the English Woodland Grant Scheme (EWGS) in 2019.</p>
</div></div>


