      <section class="brand--department-for-environment-food-rural-affairs brand__border-color organisation__brand-border-top organisation__margin-bottom" id="freedom-of-information">
    <h2 class="gem-c-heading  gem-c-heading--padding  ">Make an FOI request</h2>


    
<div class="gem-c-govspeak govuk-govspeak " data-module="govspeak">
    
        <ol class="steps">
          <li>
            Read about the Freedom of Information (FOI) Act and <a href="https://www.gov.uk/make-a-freedom-of-information-request/the-freedom-of-information-act" class="brand__color">how to make a request</a>.
          </li>
          <li>
            Check <a href="/government/publications?departments%5B%5D=rural-payments-agency&publication_type=foi-releases" class="brand__color">our previous releases</a> to see if we’ve already answered your question.
          </li>
            <li>Make a new request by contacting us using the details below.</li>
        </ol>

</div>

        <div class="organisation__contact-section ">
    <h3 class="gem-c-heading  gem-c-heading--font-size-19 gem-c-heading--padding  ">Rural Payments Agency </h3>


    <div class="grid-row">
        <address class="column-half organisation__margin-bottom organisation__address">
            Information Rights Team<br></br>Rural Payments Agency<br></br>PO Box 69<br></br>Reading<br></br>RG1 3YD<br></br>United Kingdom<br></br>
        </address>

        <div class="column-half">
            <div class="organisation__margin-bottom">
              <p>Email</p>
                <p><a class="brand__color" href="mailto:irt@rpa.gov.uk">irt@rpa.gov.uk</a></p>
            </div>


            <div class="organisation__margin-bottom">
                <p>Phone</p>
                <p class="organisation__contact-number"> 03300 416 502</p>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <p>FOI requests can be made in writing only, either by post or by email. An EIR request can be made in writing or by phone.</p>
  </div>

